      • createRowRequirement

        private RequirementOrdinary createRowRequirement(org.apache.poi.hwpf.usermodel.TableRow row,
                                                 int rowNumber,
                                                 RequirementOrdinary rowRequirement)
        Creates a row requirement if it does not exist yet

        This avoids having empty row requirements when there are no traceworthy cells in the respective row.

        Parameters:
        row - Range the new row requirement will be associated to
        rowNumber - number of the row for which to create the requirement
        rowRequirement - reference to the existing row Requirement
        Returns:
        the existing row Requirement if it already exists or a shiny new one
